<h3>
  Activation email sent to <%= user.email %>
</h3>

<p>Please check your email and follow the instructions! If you didn't receive one please wait some more minutes and be sure to check your SPAM. If everything else fails, click on the following button to resend the activation instructions:</p>

<form action="<%= resendActivationPath %>" method="post">
  <input type="submit" class="button secondary fitted" value="Resend activation email" />
</form>
